---------------------------------
 Setting up your Eclipse project
---------------------------------

Current for Eclipse 3.6:

1. Create a variable called LOCAL_REPOSITORY pointing to the place where Gradle is storing your
   cached jars
  1. Window -> Preferences
  2. Java -> Build Path -> Classpath Variables
  3. New...
  4. Name: GRADLE_REPOSITORY
  5. Path: Usually ~/.gradle/cache or ~/.something
  6. OK
